headline: Elf Beauty says short-seller report is 'without merit', analysts defend
summary: Investing.com -- ELF Beauty Inc (NYSE:ELF) said Thursday that allegations from short-seller Muddy Waters (NYSE:WAT) about overstated revenue and inflated inventory figures are "without merit."
